  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_implant">Implant</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_medical_device">MEDICAL DEVICE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_implant">Implant</xref>
 is an artificial component made from metal, high density polyethylene or ceramic to replace a diseased or worn out joint.        </p>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_implant">Implant</xref>
 may be used to replace a diseased or worn out joint in 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_joint_replacement_surgery">Joint Replacement Surgery</xref>.        </p>
